Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
deleteDeCap(25.10)                                          deleteDeCap(25.10)

Name
       deleteDeCap

Syntax
       deleteDeCap

       [-help]

       Deletes  all  decoupling capacitance cells. You can use this command to
       delete decoupling capacitance cells that you added using  the  addDeCap
       command.

Parameter
       -help  Outputs  a  brief  description of the deleteDeCap command. For a
              detailed description of the command, use the man  command:   man
              deleteDeCap.

       Example
       The  following  command deletes all of the decoupling capacitance cells
       in a design:

       deleteDeCap

Related Information
              * Placing the Design chapter in the Innovus System User Guide

                     * Adding Decoupling Capacitance

              * addDeCap

